institutions, improved turnover to Pounds 10.7m (Pounds 9.68m) reporting
operating profits of Pounds 819,000 (Pounds 1.25m losses).
Mr Inge said: 'Our investment activity was up by about a third. Consultancy
work on behalf of banks and other lending institutions continued to prosper
during the year.'
Turnover from the agricultural and residential business was virtually flat
at Pounds 14.5m (Pounds 14m) with operating profits of Pounds 458,000
against losses of Pounds 1.66m.
Net interest received was Pounds 162,000 (Pounds 48,000). The group finished
the year with Pounds 5m (Pounds 1.95m) cash and no borrowings.
