FT  13 JUL 93 / UK Company News: Halved outcome at Optometrics
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Optometrics saw pre-tax profits halved in the year ended March 31, from
Dollars 200,000 to Dollars 103,000 (Pounds 69,640).
Mr Frank Denton, chairman of this USM-traded company, said the year was one
