FT  13 JUL 93 / UK Company News: Disposal gives boost to Daejan
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Bolstered by a Pounds 2.53m surplus on the disposal of a subsidiary, pre-tax
profits of Daejan Holdings, the property group, rose by Pounds 2.8m to
Pounds 16.7m in the year to end-March.
Gross income for the year increased from Pounds 22.1m to Pounds 23m, and at
the operating level profits from continuing operations improved to Pounds
18.5m against Pounds 18.2m.
