3.5m (Pounds 5.32m).
The company said that the UK investment portfolio had been professionally
valued at the year-end and the resultant decrease of Pounds 1.1m had been
incorporated into the accounts.
A final dividend of 15p (13p) is proposed for a 27p (25p) total.
The dividend is three times covered by earnings per share of 81p.
